      "Understand IVL for calcified landing zones"
    ],
    "clinical_pearls": [
      "IVL = best for medial (Monckeberg) calcification",
      "Atherectomy only reaches intimal calcium",
      "Game-changer for calcified EVAR landing zones"
    ]
  },
